node.text: The Serena & Lily collection transforms Whitney Port’s backyard into her dream space.

node.text: 👉Swipe for the before of @samanthavarvel’s timeless kitchen. What’s your favorite part of this transformation? #serenaandlily

node.text: Designs that shine. ✨ All lighting, now up to 25% off. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 28, 2021. May be an image of flower, tree and outdoors.

node.text: This blooming hydrangea garden is the ideal spot to savor summer. ☀️ 📷: @gncgarden #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 28, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Spotlight on: The Sydney Bath Rug. 🛁  Wonderful to sink your toes into after the bath, this mat takes softness to a whole new level. Raised stripes create amazing texture, while plush tassels add a cheerful detail. Two sizes let you choose just how luxurious you want your bath to feel. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Serena & Lily on July 27, 2021 tagging @jacobsnavely, and @changoandco. May be an image of furniture and bedroom.

node.text: Sweet yet sophisticated, stylish yet practical, we love the way @changoandco brings a little more fun to this bunk room with our Hanging Rattan Chairs. 📷 @jacobsnavely #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 27, 2021. May be an image of sofa, living room and brick wall.

node.text: Ends tonight: 20% off upholstered pieces. Use code JUSTFORYOU. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Serena & Lily on July 26, 2021 tagging @designlovesdetail. May be an image of kitchen.

node.text: @designlovesdetail creates a subtle statement with a charming mix of blues and textured stone. 📷:@laceyalexander_interiors #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 26, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.

node.text: Spotlight on: The Shore Counter Stool. ✨ With sweeping curves and a classic wicker frame, Shore is a natural at elevating the counter. A comfy cushion softens the vibe – and we serve up multiple fabrics options so you can change your look with ease. A brass-finished kickplate adds a hint of shine. Dramatic? Yes. Approachable? Absolutely. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Serena & Lily on July 25, 2021 tagging @peonyinteriordesigns. May be an image of furniture and bedroom.

node.text: @peonyinteriordesigns wakes up her walls with our Luna Stripe Wallpaper. A classic from our pattern library, this print emerged from a beautiful textile Serena spotted on her travels. We opened up the design to bring a touch of the ethereal and worked with a historic wallcovering manufacturer to make sure every artful detail of the design shines through. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 25, 2021. May be an image of table and living room.

node.text: Find your new favorite breakfast spot. ☕ It all begins with a beautiful backdrop, plenty of natural texture, and touches of bright white. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Serena & Lily on July 24, 2021 tagging @loithai. May be an image of flower, tree and nature.
Photo by Serena & Lily on July 24, 2021. May be an image of living room.

node.text: A natural beauty that brings a coastal touch. Handwoven of water hyacinth – a surprisingly strong material with a soft look – our new Cape Mirror is great for bringing texture and warmth to your walls. From entryway to bedroom, it looks fabulous just about anywhere. #serenaandlily
